-- spine points, completing rate coverage so every seeded pay-scale point has a
-- salary the employment editor can auto-fill from. EffectiveFrom 2024-09-01.
--
-- WARNING: These figures are PROVISIONAL / best-effort. The Rest of England
-- column is a base value and the Inner / Outer / Fringe columns add a flat area
-- supplement (Inner +6,300, Outer +4,200, Fringe +1,300) rather than the exact
-- gazetted area figures. Verify and replace EVERY value against the official
-- 2024-25 STPCD before any payroll-facing use. Revaluation closes existing rows
-- (EffectiveTo = day before the new rates take effect) and inserts new ones --
-- never UPDATE AnnualSalary in place.
-- ============================================================================

